{"DELL":[{"def":"A small, retired valley; a ravine.","pos":""},{"def":"A young woman; a wench.","pos":""}],"DELLA CRUSCA":[{"def":"A shortened form of Academia della Crusca, an academy in Florescence, Italy, founded in the 16th century, especially for conversing the purity of the Italian language.","pos":""}],"DELLACRUSCAN":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to the Accademia della Crusca in Florence.","pos":""}]}